  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\nIf user sends a message just after he was joined to public chat - his userpic is not shown for both messages (system and sent).\r\nSo if sender of the message is the same that in last system message - userpic is not shown.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nAvatar is shown\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n<img width=\"226\" alt=\"photo_2019-11-19 16 08 54 jpeg 2019-11-19 16-09-16\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/69158601-fd7ffa00-0ae6-11ea-8753-8223e5b06ab5.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- User B: Open Status\r\n- User B: Create group chat with user A\r\n- User A: join the group chat and send a message\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\r\n- Status version: nightly 18/11/2019\r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n",
